snippet.title: Caves of Qud 1.0 - Official Announcement Trailer, with Kitfox Games
snippet.description:
Live and drink, friend. Kitfox Games is excited to announce that we are the publishers of Caves of Qud. We are teaming up with developer Freehold Games for 1.0 release in 2024. Learn more: https://bit.ly/3DxY9LY


Narrator: Justice Washington (https://justicewashington.net/)
Music: Craig Hamilton (https://soundcloud.com/craigoryham)

http://www.freeholdgames.com
